content:
Manage Your SMS Request and Flow Experience

You can now save your work while requesting a new 10-digit long code, brand, or campaign. Enable Flow for your SMS sends in Unified Messaging.

Where: These changes apply to Salesforce Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Marketing Cloud Growth Edition.

Save Your SMS Drafts
Save a draft and submit your request at another time. Your drafts are auto-saved every minute.

Enable SMS Usage in Flow for Unified Messaging
Specify that an SMS code can send and receive messages using Flow, enabling it to maintain conversations with customers.
title: Save Drafts and Enable Flow for SMS Requests in Marketing Cloud
